728988f-a.title: Richmond: Hylan Boulevard - Bedell Avenue
728988f-a.text:
Hylan Boulevard, south side, between Bedell and Page
Avenues, showing the south side of the Manee Bouse. The house
is 100 yards south of the Boulevard.
August 27, 1930.
P. L. Sperr
(2)
A view of the west side of the house.
Augst 27, 1930.
P. L. Sperr
